api_list.name: Check lottery
api_list.description: Check lottery - ตรวจหวย
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://thai-lottery3.p.rapidapi.com/v1/lottery/check"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "thai-lottery3.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
